caption: A detailed, close-up studio shot of a single piece of dark black volcanic lava rock (scoria). The rock is highly porous and vesicular, with a rough, abrasive texture filled with many irregular holes
A computer vision teacher, smiling at the camera

A studio shot of a black Pilot 400 permanent marker. The marker has a black body and cap, with white and grey text reading 'PILOT PERMANENT MARKER 400'. The cap indicates a 'Broad / Chisel' tip with gold text. The marker is shown at an angle, isolated on a plain white background.
A matte black, full-face motorcycle helmet with a dark tinted visor and an angular chin guard, isolated on a white background.

A person wearing jeans and red work gloves operates a red and grey electric demolition hammer with a tamper foot attachment. The tool is being used on the ground, which is covered in gravel and broken cinder blocks.
A pair of light blue wash, wide-leg jeans, isolated on a plain white background.

A standard green table tennis table with a net dividing the center. Two red paddles and a white ball are resting on the far side of the table. The table has a metal frame with wheels and is isolated on a plain white background.
A Pokemon Trading Card Game booster pack from the 'Scarlet & Violet: Paldean Fates' (Destino di Paldea) expansion, featuring Pikachu as the cover art. The pack is isolated on a plain white background
A black and silver espresso machine on a wooden kitchen counter, brewing two shots of espresso simultaneously into small glass cups.
A 'Molten' brand basketball, model BG4000, with 'FIBA APPROVED' text printed on it, isolated on a plain white background.
classic blue box of Barilla brand 'Spaghetti N5' pasta, featuring the red oval logo prominently in the center over a graphic of uncooked spaghetti strands
A kidney-shaped swimming pool with bright blue water in a backyard garden. It is surrounded by a gravel patio and a green lawn
The flag of Palestine, featuring three horizontal stripes of black, white, and green, with a red triangle on the hoist
Three round, disc-shaped ceramic components of different sizes, with white tops and dark sides
A red BMW F 650 dual-sport motorcycle parked on a patch of grass next to a low wooden fence. The motorcycle has a tall windscreen and a black top case mounted on the rear
Il Gabibbo, a red, bulbous puppet character with large cartoon eyes, wearing white tuxedo cuffs and a matching bowtie, lying on its side in a reclining pose and pointing upwards

A photograph of Mikhail Gorbachev wearing a dark suit, white shirt, red tie, and aviator-style eyeglasses. He has his prominent port-wine stain birthmark on his forehead and is wearing a wired earpiece, likely for translation.

A classic round analog wall clock with a black rim and a white face. It has large, bold black Arabic numerals. The black hour hand points to 10 and the black minute hand points to 2, showing the time as 10:10

The vinyl record album cover for 'Orbit Orbit' by Caparezzza, featuring sci-fi artwork of an astronaut walking on an alien planet with a spaceship and a ringed planet in the background. Two black vinyl records are shown next to the sleeve
